    "Therefore, LLMs will exhibit bias and produce content that will be toxic to certain groups and yet align with the values of other groups.",
    "In general, AI developers want models to achieve the 3H qualities, which means that they should be harmless, helpful, and honest.",
    "However, those three qualities can mean different things to different people.",
    "Therefore, LLM alignment and the development of ethical standards for AI will be an ongoing challenge and are active areas of research.",
